Knowledge Check
What's the difference between podman save and podman export?
How would you verify the integrity of a saved tarball?
When would you choose commit over building with a Dockerfile?
Answers:

save works with images (preserving layers/metadata), export works with containers (filesystem only)
Checksum verification: sha256sum alpine_backup.tar
When you need to preserve runtime state or don't have the Dockerfile
